**Status: DRAFT — not yet effective.** This version was rewritten to describe the system FactHarbor **actually operates today**: an invite-gated claim-analysis service, not a community-contribution platform. Items marked **[NEEDS DECISION: …]** require a human/legal decision before this policy is published. This draft has been reviewed internally and by an external-counsel-style AI pass (GPT-5.5); it has **not** been signed off by retained Swiss counsel, which remains a launch blocker (see [[Operational Readiness>>FactHarbor.Organisation.Governance.Operational Readiness.WebHome]] §2.1).
